tainer\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To ensure <strong data-start=\"1482\" data-end=\"1505\">maximum credibility<\/strong>, Clarity AI combines <strong data-start=\"1527\" data-end=\"1553\">AI-driven verification<\/strong> with <strong data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1578\">human oversight<\/strong>.<\/p><p data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1605\">\ud83d\udc49 <strong data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1603\">How it works:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"1606\" data-end=\"1805\"><li data-start=\"1606\" data-end=\"1707\">AI <strong data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1639\">analyzes historical data<\/strong> to detect <strong data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1704\">fake promotions, inconsistencies, and bot activity<\/strong>.<\/li><li data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1805\">If suspicious behavior is detected, the case is flagged for <strong data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1802\">manual review by our experts<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-822fd1e elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"822fd1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b7a237 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8b7a237\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3. Secure Payment System (Escrow)<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d570eab elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d570eab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"2482\" data-end=\"2606\">Since Clarity AI operates on <strong data-start=\"84\" data-end=\"94\">Solana<\/strong>, the escrow and payment system is fully <strong data-start=\"135\" data-end=\"147\">on-chain<\/strong>, ensuring secure and transparent transactions between investors and KOLs. Instead of traditional Ethereum-based smart contracts, we use <strong data-start=\"284\" data-end=\"325\">Solana Program Library (SPL) programs<\/strong> to handle payments efficiently with <strong data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"399\" data-is-only-node=\"\">low fees and high-speed execution<\/strong>.<\/p><p data-start=\"2608\" data-end=\"2630\">\ud83d\udc49 <strong data-start=\"2611\" data-end=\"2628\">How it works:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2860\"><li data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2701\"><strong data-start=\"432\" data-end=\"453\">Wallet Connection<\/strong> \u2013 Users connect their <strong data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"522\">Phantom, Solflare, or other Solana wallets<\/strong> to the Clarity AI platform.<\/li><li data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2701\"><strong data-start=\"555\" data-end=\"581\">On-Chain Data Fetching<\/strong> \u2013 The platform reads data directly from <strong data-start=\"622\" data-end=\"645\">Solana\u2019s blockchain<\/strong> using <strong data-start=\"652\" data-end=\"665\" data-is-only-node=\"\">RPC calls<\/strong>.<\/li><li data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2701\"><strong data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"696\">Smart Contract Escrow<\/strong> \u2013 Payments are locked in an escrow <strong data-start=\"732\" data-end=\"753\">SPL token account<\/strong> until conditions are met.<\/li><li data-start=\"2631\" data-end=\"2701\"><strong data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"805\">Trustless Payouts<\/strong> \u2013 Funds are only released when the <strong data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"874\">job is confirmed as completed<\/strong>. If not, <strong data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"907\">buyers get a refund<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ul><p><br \/>Once a <strong data-start=\"917\" data-end=\"926\">buyer<\/strong> initiates a payment to a KOL, the transaction is recorded <strong data-start=\"985\" data-end=\"1011\">on Solana\u2019s blockchain<\/strong>, ensuring full transparency. Funds remain in <strong data-start=\"1057\" data-end=\"1067\">escrow<\/strong> until the buyer manually confirms the service has been delivered. If a dispute arises, Clarity AI\u2019s <strong data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1210\">AI-driven analysis &amp; human review team<\/strong> ensures fair resolution.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c654047 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c654047\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 data-start=\"2187\" data-end=\"2227\"><strong data-start=\"2191\" data-end=\"2227\">\ud83d\ude80 Escrow Workflow on Clarity AI<\/strong><\/h3><p data-start=\"2228\" data-end=\"2604\">1\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong data-start=\"2232\" data-end=\"2262\">User connects their wallet<\/strong> and selects a KOL.<br data-start=\"2281\" data-end=\"2284\" \/>2\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong data-start=\"2288\" data-end=\"2337\">Buyer deposits funds into the escrow contract<\/strong>, locking the amount until the job is done.<br data-start=\"2380\" data-end=\"2383\" \/>3\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong data-start=\"2387\" data-end=\"2416\">KOL completes the service<\/strong>, and the buyer marks it as &#8220;Completed&#8221;.<br data-start=\"2456\" data-end=\"2459\" \/>4\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong data-start=\"2463\" data-end=\"2515\">Clarity AI\u2019s smart contract releases the payment<\/strong> to the KOL.<br data-start=\"2527\" data-end=\"2530\" \/>5\ufe0f\u20e3 If the KOL <strong data-start=\"2545\" data-end=\"2565\">fails to deliver<\/strong>, the buyer can trigger a <strong data-start=\"2591\" data-end=\"2601\">refund<\/strong>.<\/p><p data-start=\"2606\" data-end=\"2766\">Since <strong data-start=\"2612\" data-end=\"2659\">Solana\u2019s transaction fees are extremely low<\/strong>, the escrow process is <strong data-start=\"2683\" data-end=\"2713\">cost-effective and instant<\/strong>, making it <strong data-start=\"2725\" data-end=\"2765\">superior to Ethereum-based solutions<\/strong>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7af8feb elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"7af8feb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43ba88b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"43ba88b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">4. All-In-One Web Platform<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-277b3c5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"277b3c5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"3800\" data-end=\"3924\">Clarity AI is built as a <strong data-start=\"3825\" data-end=\"3847\">web-based platform<\/strong>, meaning you can access it <strong data-start=\"3875\" data-end=\"3896\">anytime, anywhere<\/strong> without downloading an app.<\/p><p data-start=\"3926\" data-end=\"3948\">\ud83d\udc49 <strong data-start=\"3929\" data-end=\"3946\">How it works:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"3949\" data-end=\"4182\"><li data-start=\"3949\" data-end=\"4029\">The entire system runs <strong data-start=\"3974\" data-end=\"3990\">in the cloud<\/strong>, optimized for <strong data-start=\"4006\" data-end=\"4026\">desktop &amp; mobile<\/strong>.<\/li><li data-start=\"4030\" data-end=\"4097\">The user interface is designed for <strong data-start=\"4067\" data-end=\"4094\">simplicity &amp; efficiency<\/strong>.<\/li><li data-start=\"4098\" data-end=\"4182\">Works seamlessly with <strong data-start=\"4122\" data-end=\"4140\">crypto wallets<\/strong> and <strong data-start=\"4145\" data-end=\"4158\">data APIs<\/strong> for real-time tracking.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a3d5f6 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"2a3d5f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2fcd1a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2fcd1a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Final Summary<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15856c1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"15856c1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"3800\" data-end=\"3924\">\ud83d\udd25 Clarity AI is <strong data-start=\"4877\" data-end=\"4906\">more than just a platform<\/strong>\u2014it\u2019s a <strong data-start=\"4914\" data-end=\"4951\">revolution in crypto transparency<\/strong>.<br data-start=\"4952\" data-end=\"4955\" \/>\ud83d\udd0e <strong data-start=\"4958\" data-end=\"5037\">Track influencers, verify deals, and secure transactions like never before.<\/strong><br data-start=\"5037\" data-end=\"5040\" \/>\ud83d\ude80 <strong data-start=\"5043\" data-end=\"5111\">No risks, no scams\u2014only real data, real trust, and real results.<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7af460 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e7af460\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1916\" height=\"1493\" src=\"https:\/\/clarity-ai.pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/roadmap-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-141\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/clarity-ai.pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/roadmap-1.png 1916w, https:\/\/clarity-ai.pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/roadmap-1-300x234.png 300w, https:\/\/clarity-ai.pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/roadmap-1-1024x798.png 1024w, https:\/\/clarity-ai.pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/roadmap-1-768x598.png 768w, https:\/\/clarity-ai.pro\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/roadmap-1-1536x1197.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1916px) 100vw, 1916px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a4fade e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7a4fade\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-313c02c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"313c02c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_ty